  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Part-Time Service Crew & Kitchen Crew",
  "description": "<p><strong>We’re Expanding Our Team — Part-Time Service Crew & Kitchen Crew Wanted!</strong></p><p><strong>If you enjoy being part of a lively environment, love good food, and take pride in your work, we’d love to meet you. Whether you shine at the front of house or thrive in the kitchen, there’s a place for you here.</strong></p><p><strong>Salary Range: $15-$18/hour</strong></p><p><strong>Schedule: 3-4days work week, Around 6 hours per shift</strong></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>Service Crew — What You’ll Do</strong></p><p>Welcome guests with a friendly attitude</p><p>Take and process orders accurately</p><p>Serve food and drinks efficiently</p><p>Keep the dining area clean and organised</p><p>Assist with daily operational duties whenever needed</p><p></p><p><strong>Kitchen Crew — What You’ll Do</strong></p><p>Help with opening and closing preparations</p><p>Handle food prep and portioning based on SOPs</p><p>Work across different kitchen stations</p><p>Maintain cleanliness and safety standards</p><p>Adapt well to a warm, fast-paced kitchen environment<br /></p><p><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>No prior experience needed — we will train you</p><p>Comfortable with rotating shifts, weekends, and public holidays</p><p>Positive, approachable, and team-focused</p><p>Able to multitask and stay calm during peak hours</p><p>Willing to learn and grow in the F&B industry</p><p></p><p><strong>Whether you’re passionate about creating a great customer experience or prefer being hands-on with food preparation, we offer a supportive space where you can grow your skills and build your career.</strong></p><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>If you’re energetic, dependable, and ready to be part of a motivated team — send in your application today!</strong></p>",
